# 1


```
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant C as Container<br>(172.17.0.2)
    participant H as Host OS & iptables<br>(172.25.110.76)
    participant I as Internet<br>(8.8.8.8)

    Note over C,I: --- THE ORIGINAL DIRECTION (REQUEST) ---
    
    C->>H: ICMP Request<br/>[Src: 172.17.0.2] -> [Dst: 8.8.8.8]
    Note over H: MASQUERADE (SNAT)<br/>Log to conntrack table
    H->>I: ICMP Request<br/>[Src: 172.25.110.76] -> [Dst: 8.8.8.8]

    Note over C,I: --- THE REPLY DIRECTION (RESPONSE) ---
    
    I-->>H: ICMP Reply<br/>[Src: 8.8.8.8] -> [Dst: 172.25.110.76]
    Note over H: Check conntrack table<br/>Implicit Reverse SNAT
    H-->>C: ICMP Reply<br/>[Src: 8.8.8.8] -> [Dst: 172.17.0.2]
```


